10 ounce Chicken Cutlets
5.25 ounce Cabbage & Carrots
0.1 ounce Dried Shiitake Mushrooms
¾ ounce Coconut Aminos
3.5 ounce Lacinato Kale
1.75 ounce Ginger-Lime Vinaigrette
¾ teaspoon Chili & Ginger Spice Rub
1 ounce Spicy Ginger-Lime Aïoli
½ ounce Sliced Almonds
1 unit Scallions
Cooking Oil
Salt

Please refer to the recipe card for Step 1.